PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773839493
OL,3,CGrieving mother begs government to
OL,4,C'find some money' for meningitis
OL,5,Cvaccine
OL,7,FThe mother of an 18-year-old student
OL,8,Fwho died from meningitis says the
OL,9,Fgovernment need to "find some money to
OL,10,Froll out this vaccine for meningitis".
OL,12,FMarissa Mullans lost her son Alfie to
OL,13,Fmeningitis B in June 2023, 14 hours
OL,14,Fafter he was taken to A&E.
OL,16,FSince his death she has been
OL,17,Fcampaigning to get the government to
OL,18,Fstart an awareness campaign to inform
OL,19,Fparents that many of their children
OL,20,Fare not vaccinated against meningitis
OL,21,FB.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773839493
OL,3,CGrieving mother begs government to
OL,4,C'find some money' for meningitis
OL,5,Cvaccine
OL,7,FAny young people born before 2015 will
OL,8,Fnot be protected, unless they had the
OL,9,Fvaccination privately.
OL,11,FHer plea follows the outbreak of
OL,12,Fmeningitis in Kent, where two young
OL,13,Fpeople have died and others are in
OL,14,Fhospital.
OL,16,FSome cases have been confirmed as
OL,17,Fmeningitis B, health officials have
OL,18,Fsaid, as hundreds of people are being
OL,19,Furged to get antibiotics to stem the
OL,20,Fspread of infection.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773839493
OL,3,CGrieving mother begs government to
OL,4,C'find some money' for meningitis
OL,5,Cvaccine
OL,7,FMarissa said: "It's exactly what I was
OL,8,Fraising awareness to try and prevent.
OL,10,F"It's absolutely heartbreaking and my
OL,11,Fheart goes out to all of the families
OL,12,Faffected in Kent.
OL,14,F"The government needs to do something
OL,15,Fand they need to do it now to protect
OL,16,Fyoung people's lives.
OL,18,F"Age is a protected characteristic,
OL,19,Fbut they're discriminating against our
OL,20,Fyoung people based on the year they
OL,21,Fwere born.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773839493
OL,3,CGrieving mother begs government to
OL,4,C'find some money' for meningitis
OL,5,Cvaccine
OL,7,F"'If you were born after 2015, we'll
OL,8,Fprotect you'. Those that were born
OL,9,Fbefore that are now going to college
OL,10,Fand universities, 'we're not going to
OL,11,Fprotect you'."
OL,13,FITV News Granada Reports Correspondent
OL,14,FMel Barham explains why the year you
OL,15,Fwere born is important, as well as the
OL,16,Fsigns to watch out for.
OL,18,FMarissa described Alfie, who was
OL,19,Fstudying at Bury College, as "the most
OL,20,Fperfect son".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773839493
OL,3,CGrieving mother begs government to
OL,4,C'find some money' for meningitis
OL,5,Cvaccine
OL,7,FHe became unwell in June 2023, and
OL,8,Fdied after being taken to hospital.
OL,10,FAlfie did not show many of the
OL,11,Fsymptoms often linked to meningitis,
OL,12,Fbut he returned from college with a
OL,13,Fheadache.
OL,15,FMarissa said: "He didn't feel too
OL,16,Fgreat so he was going to go and have a
OL,17,Flie down".
OL,19,F"We noticed a tiny little rash about
OL,20,Fthe size of a 5 pence piece on Alfie's
OL,21,Fchest."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773839493
OL,3,CGrieving mother begs government to
OL,4,C'find some money' for meningitis
OL,5,Cvaccine
OL,7,FMarissa said they began to think then
OL,8,Fthat it could be meningitis, and took
OL,9,FAlfie to A&E where they took him to
OL,10,Fthe resuscitation unit. On the way
OL,11,Fthere, Marissa said Alfie "was purple
OL,12,Ffrom head to toe".
OL,14,FShe said: "I remember asking the nurse
OL,15,Fif he's going to be okay, and the
OL,16,Fnurse responded 'we're going to do
OL,17,Feverything we can' and it was at that
OL,18,Fmoment... you don't want to hear that
OL,19,Ffrom a nurse," she said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773839493
OL,3,CGrieving mother begs government to
OL,4,C'find some money' for meningitis
OL,5,Cvaccine
OL,7,FMarissa added: "The consultant came
OL,8,Fout to say that Alfie's heart had
OL,9,Fstopped. I think I was just in shock
OL,10,Fat that point, so I did go back into
OL,11,Fthe room and I stood there and watched
OL,12,Fthem working on Alfie for about half
OL,13,Fan hour... and then they called time".
OL,15,F"My son had aspirations for his
OL,16,Ffuture. He wanted to join the
OL,17,Fmilitary. He wanted to go in and be a
OL,18,FRoyal Engineer. He wanted to serve for
OL,19,Fthis country.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773839493
OL,3,CGrieving mother begs government to
OL,4,C'find some money' for meningitis
OL,5,Cvaccine
OL,7,F"But this country has made a decision
OL,8,Fthat my son's life isn't cost
OL,9,Feffective, and that needs to stop, and
OL,10,Fit needs to stop now."
OL,12,FMarissa has started a petition to
OL,13,Foffer the meningitis B vaccine to all
OL,14,F16 to 23 year olds, not just those
OL,15,Fborn after September 2015.
OL,17,FShe said: "If anybody could sign the
OL,18,Fpetition, I would really appreciate it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773839493
OL,3,CGrieving mother begs government to
OL,4,C'find some money' for meningitis
OL,5,Cvaccine
OL,7,F"Keir Starmer and Wes Streeting have
OL,8,Fthe opportunity to sit with the JVCI,
OL,9,Fre-evaluate, find some money, and roll
OL,10,Fout that vaccine to prevent this from
OL,11,Fhappening again.
OL,13,F"It isn't unprecedented, this has
OL,14,Fhappened before. My child has lost his
OL,15,Flife. Countless other parents have
OL,16,Flost their children's lives.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773839493
OL,3,CGrieving mother begs government to
OL,4,C'find some money' for meningitis
OL,5,Cvaccine
OL,7,F"We know when people come to
OL,8,Funiversity, they come from all around
OL,9,Fthe UK and they move into halls of
OL,10,Fresidence. Living in close proximity
OL,11,Fis a breeding ground for meningitis B.
OL,12,FThis is how we end up with this."
OL,14,FSpeaking at a press conference, Health
OL,15,FSecretary Wes Streeting said he has
OL,16,Fasked Joint Committee on Vaccination
OL,17,Fand Immunisation to review its policy
OL,18,Fon a vaccination programme.
OL,20,FSymptoms of meningitis
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
